summary:
14. Exempts supplies and technical assistance to the Transitional Federal Government for security sector development from sanctions;

15. Requests the African Union to maintain and enhance AMISOM's deployment;

16. Authorizes AMISOM's maintenance until 31 January 2010;

17. Requests logistical support for AMISOM until 31 January 2010;

18. Requests AMISOM to ensure transparent use of equipment and services;

19. Requests the Secretary-General to provide technical advice to the African Union;

20. Urges Member States to contribute to the UN Trust Fund for AMISOM;

21. Requests the Secretary-General to coordinate UN activities in Somalia;

22. Requests the Secretary-General to support the Transitional Federal Government on human rights;

23. Requests expedited deployment of UNPOS and other UN offices;

24. Decides to remain seized of the matter.
